originalSql:
SELECT 
    p.Id AS PostId,
    p.Title,
    p.CreationDate,
    p.Score,
    p.ViewCount,
    u.DisplayName AS OwnerDisplayName,
    u.Reputation AS OwnerReputation,
    ARRAY_AGG(t.TagName) AS Tags,
    COUNT(v.Id) AS VoteCount
FROM 
    Posts p
JOIN 
    Users u ON p.OwnerUserId = u.Id
LEFT JOIN 
    Tags t ON t.ExcerptPostId = p.Id
LEFT JOIN 
    Votes v ON v.PostId = p.Id
WHERE 
    p.CreationDate >= '2023-01-01' 
GROUP BY 
    p.Id, p.Title, p.CreationDate, p.Score, p.ViewCount, u.DisplayName, u.Reputation
ORDER BY 
    p.CreationDate DESC
LIMIT 100

RIGHT JOIN (SELECT "t0"."Id", "t0"."PostTypeId", "t0"."AcceptedAnswerId", "t0"."ParentId", "t0"."CreationDate", "t0"."Score", "t0"."ViewCount", "t0"."Body", "t0"."OwnerUserId", "t0"."OwnerDisplayName", "t0"."LastEditorUserId", "t0"."LastEditorDisplayName", "t0"."LastEditDate", "t0"."LastActivityDate", "t0"."Title", "t0"."Tags", "t0"."AnswerCount", "t0"."CommentCount", "t0"."FavoriteCount", "t0"."ClosedDate", "t0"."CommunityOwnedDate", "t0"."ContentLicense", "Users"."Id" AS "Id0", "Users"."Reputation", "Users"."CreationDate" AS "CreationDate0", "Users"."DisplayName", "Users"."LastAccessDate", "Users"."WebsiteUrl", "Users"."Location", "Users"."AboutMe", "Users"."Views", "Users"."UpVotes", "Users"."DownVotes", "Users"."ProfileImageUrl", "Users"."AccountId", "s1"."Id" AS "Id1", "s1"."TagName", "s1"."Count", "s1"."ExcerptPostId", "s1"."WikiPostId", "s1"."IsModeratorOnly", "s1"."IsRequired"
FROM "Users"
INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM "Posts"
WHERE "CreationDate" >= TIMESTAMP '2023-01-01 00:00:00') AS "t0" ON "Users"."Id" = "t0"."OwnerUserId"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "t0"."Id" = "s1"."ExcerptPostId") AS "t1" ON "Votes"."PostId" = "t1"."Id"
GROUP BY "t1"."Id", "t1"."CreationDate", "t1"."Score", "t1"."ViewCount", "t1"."Title", "t1"."Reputation", "t1"."DisplayName"
ORDER BY "t1"."CreationDate" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 100) AS "t5"
